      m_SubObjectType: 
      m_EditorAssetChanged: 0
    videoFileName: "01_\u6708\u4E0B\u8AC7\u611B.mov"
    lyrics: "\"Yo pasi\u2019amis a yo pasitimol, o masarakesay ya o masarakesay ya
      o mamikuli.\nKuliay ya kuliay i takuwanan, hay ya mapolong a matayal.\nYo pasi\u2019amis
      yo pasiitip, icoway ko nengnengen no wali wawa?\nYo melimeli yo melimeli, koyosay
      to tino kayoing, o cimay hakiya?\nYo pasi\u2019etip a yo pasitimol, icoway
      ko nengnengen no wali wawa?\nYo felatfelat sa yo felatfelat, koya alopong no
      kayoing, o cimay hakiya?\nTangasa i wali nosi no lotok, ccay ko fulad a sanasengseng
      ya u karaw iso.\nU karaw ya u karaw no tatusaay, naw\u2019ay naw\u2019ay ya
      sa kako.\nTangasa i tokos misano lutung, yosi ko ocinara ca\u2019 sano ngaci
      u pising iso.\nU pising ya u pising no tatusaay, ay ya ay ya kako lina.\nYo
      pasi\u2019amis yo pasitimol, o masarekesay o masarekesay o mamikuli.\nKuliay
      ya kuliay i takuwanan, hay ya mapolong hay ya matayal.\""
    interactionVisibleLyricRings: 0100000003000000
