    videoFileName: "02_\u795D\u8C50\u5E74.mov"
    lyrics: "Hay yo i yi ay ya ay ya ya yen,\nhay yan na i yo ay yen hoy yan na i
      ya hay yan,\nhay yan na i ya ay yan ho ay yan,\nhan hi yen ay yan a hi yan
      ay hi\u2019n, hoy yen han yo in i ya ay yay.\nHo i yi yan i yi yan na i ye,\nhay
      yan na i ya hay yan ho ay yan na hi yan hay hi\u2019,\nhay yan na i yan hay
      yan ho ay yan,\nhan hi yan hi yan na hi yan hay hi\u2019n, hoy yan han hi ya
      on hay hi\u2019n i ya hay yay.\nHay yo i hi hay ya hay hayng ya,\nhoy yan na
      i yo i yen hoy yan na i ya hay yan,\nhay yan na i ya ay yen ho ay yan,\nhan
      hi yan hi yan na i yan hay hi\u2019n, hoy yin han yo in hi ya hoy yan.\nHo
      i yi yan i yi yan na i hi\u2019y,\nhay yan na i ya hay yan ho ay yan na hi
      yan hay hi\u2019,\nhay yan na i yan hay yan ho ay yan,\nhan hi yan hi yan na
      hi yan hay hi\u2019n, hi\u2019y yan han hi ya on hay hi\u2019n i ya hay yay."
    interactionVisibleLyricRings: 0100000003000000
