    videoFileName: "06_\u9664\u8349\u6B4C.mov"
    lyrics: "Hay ya hikasi hikasi i kalaloman, malingad talomah kami \u2019alayay
      to takuyodan,\nhoy ya tahila i omah sato kami, tatuyay to raral kami kulasay
      to pakreng.\nHoy yo minukay sato dadaya kami, tayra i Piwma kami patawsi sato
      kami,\nhay ya minukay marasang sato kami, tahira i loma\u2019 kami mapoi\u2019
      ko fafahi.\nHay ya mahalek malafi sato kami, ci dateng sato kami o futing no
      acawa.\nHay ya hikasi hikasi i kalaloman, malingad talomah kami kalicay i paliding,\nhoy
      yo tahila i omah sato kami, tangsol maepod kami panayay to pakreng.\nHoy ya
      ila to kiya heci noya panay, cecayay a sato kiya heci niya panay sano niyam,\nhoy
      yo minukay sato dadaya kami, tahira i loma\u2019 kami filoay ya matifek.\nHay
      ya mahalek malafi sato kami, ci dateng sato kami o cekiw no acawa."
    interactionVisibleLyricRings: 0100000003000000
